quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,Humne Nooh ko uski qaum ki taraf bheja (is hidayat ke saath) ke apni qaum ke logon ko khabardar karde qabl iske ke unpar ek dardnaak azaab aaye
  71,2,"Usne kaha “ Aey meri qaum ke logon, main tumhare liye ek saaf saaf khabardar kardene wala (paighambar) hoon"
  71,3,(Tumko aagah karta hoon) ke Allah ki bandagi karo aur ussey daro aur meri itaat (follow) karo
  71,4,Allah tumhare gunaahon se darguzar farmayega aur tumhein ek waqt-e-mukarrar tak baaki rakkhega. Haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ka mukarrar kiya hua waqt jab aa jata hai to phir taala nahin jata kaash tumhein iska ilm ho
  71,5,"Usne arz kiya “Aey mere Rubb , maine apni qaum ke logon ko shab-o-roz (night and day) pukara"
  71,6,Magar meri pukar ne unke farar hi mei izafa kiya
  71,7,"Aur jab bhi maine unko bulaya taa-ke tu unhein maaf karde , unhon ne kaano mein ungliyan thoos li aur apne kapdon se mooh dhaank liye aur apni rawish par adh gaye aur bada takabbur (proudness) kiya"
  71,8,Phir maine unko haanke pukarey (openly) ki dawat di
  71,9,Phir maine aelaniya (publicly) bhi unko tableeg ki aur chupke chupke bhi samjhaya
  71,10,"Maine kaha apne Rubb se maafi maango,beshak woh bada maaf karne wala hai"
  71,11,Woh tumpar aasmaan se khoob baarishein barsayega
  71,12,"Tumhein maal aur aulad se nawaze ga, tumhare liye baagh paida karega aur tumhare liye nehrein jaari kardega"
  71,13,Tumhein kya ho gaya hai ke Allah ke liye tum kisi waqar (majesty) ki tawakku nahin rakhte
  71,14,Halaanke usne tarah tarah se tumhein banaya hai
  71,15,Kya dekhte nahin ho ke Allah ne kis tarah saat aasman teh-bar-teh banaye
  71,16,Aur unmein chand ko noor aur suraj ko chiraag banaya
  71,17,Aur Allah ne tumko zameen se ajeeb tarah ugaya
  71,18,Phir woh tumhein isi zameen mein wapas le jayega aur issey yakayak tumko nikal khada karega
  71,19,Aur Allah ne zameen ko tumhare liye farsh ki tarah bicha diya
  71,20,Taa-ke tum uske andar khule raaston mein chalo
  71,21,"Nooh ne kaha “mere Rubb, unhon ne meri baat radd kardi aur un (raheeson) ki pairvi ki jo maal aur aulad paa kar aur zyada na murad ho gaye hain"
  71,22,In logon ne bada bhaari makr (plot) ka jaal phaila rakkha hai
  71,23,"Inhon ne kaha hargiz na chodo apne maboodon (deities) ko, aur na chodo Wadd aur Suwa ko aur na Yagus aur Yaook aur Nasr ko (idol names)"
  71,24,"Inhon ne bahut logon ko gumraah kiya hai, aur tu bhi in zalimon ko gumrahi ke siwa kisi cheez mein tarakki na de"
  71,25,"Apni khataon ki bina par hi woh garq(drown) kiye gaye aur Aag mein jhoonk diye gaye , phir unhon ne apne liye Allah se bachane wala koi madadgar na paya"
  71,26,"Aur Nooh ne kaha “Mere Rubb, In kafiron mein se koi zameen par basne wala na chodh"
  71,27,Agar tu ne inko chodh diya to yeh tere bandon ko gumraah karenge aur inki nasal se jo bhi paida hoga badkar aur sakht kafir hi hoga
  71,28,"Mere Rubb, mujhey aur mere waldain ko aur har us shaks ko jo mere ghar mein momin ki haisiyat se dakhil hua hai, Aur sab momin mardon aur auraton ko maaf farma de, Aur zalimon ke liye halakat ke siwa kisi cheez mein izafa na kar"